Troubleshooting Tips
Out of Memory Errors:

Reduce spark.driver.memory to 2g if system has limited RAM
Decrease dataset size in generator (e.g., 1 million records)
Increase spark.sql.shuffle.partitions to 16
Slow Performance:

Ensure caching is implemented for reused DataFrames
Check partition count matches available CPU cores
Use explain() method to view query plans
File Not Found Errors:

Verify CSV file was generated successfully
Check file paths are relative to script location
Ensure output directories are created automatically
Java Heap Space Errors:

export SPARK_DRIVER_MEMORY=2g
export SPARK_EXECUTOR_MEMORY=2g
